<br>
I chose Erudite because of int and popped my gamma crrection up for night. 154 int at level 14, and i havent got a stein of moggok yet. This guy has a shovel of ponz  (higher mage helped me with it!)  So I have decent STR, im currently hunting in the Overthere, and bieng slightly evil, or having &quot;Rude Manners&quot; i can sell there. Bad manners are like having apprehensive and indiff almost everywhere. IMHO i think Eruds are the best, simply ride over to Qeynos for a newbie area lasting til about 8, then tp to Freeport on orcs til 11, Dervs til 14, Orc Hyway in oasis til 18, overthere til 22. Good luck to ya mages!<br>
<br>
(PS Gnomes tinker, High Elves are great at trade skills, DEs get ultravision righht away, Eruds have highest int, but i cant think of anything too useful for human mages except good faction....) <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showPrevMessage?topicID=128.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showNextMessage?topicID=128.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=128.topic&index=6><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.threadControl?topicID=128.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/unread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=128.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=128.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub102.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="themagicianstowerannouncements">Administration<option value="themagicianstowergeneral">General<option value="themagicianstowerfrm32">Class Balance<option value="themagicianstowerfrm45">User Interface<option value="themagicianstowersp